<section class="section legal-info">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-grid">
      <div class="content-image">
        <div class="image-placeholder">
          <span>✅</span>
          <p>Lab-Tested Quality Guaranteed</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="content-text">
        <span class="section-label">NO BS QUALITY</span>
        <h2>Premium Weed — Not Premium Prices</h2>
        <p>
          Here's the thing: good cannabis shouldn't require a second mortgage. We've cut out the middlemen, the fancy storefronts, and the marketing fluff. What's left? Quality product at prices that make sense.
        </p>
        <p>
          Based in Mullaways, NSW, we're not some faceless corporation. We're Aussies who got tired of the industry BS and decided to do something about it. Every product is lab-tested — because you deserve to know exactly what you're putting in your body.
        </p>
        <p>
          What you get when you order from us:
        </p>
        <ul class="compliance-list">
          <li>Actual lab results — THC/CBD content, purity testing, the works</li>
          <li>Transparent pricing — no "contact us" games, prices are on the page</li>
          <li>Age verification (18+) — we don't cut corners on this</li>
          <li>Discreet shipping with full tracking — your business, not your neighbours'</li>
          <li>Support from humans who actually know the products</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          <a href="/how-it-works" class="text-link">See how it works →</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .legal-info {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .content-text h2 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 25px;
  }

  .content-text p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .content-text a.text-link {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .content-text a.text-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .compliance-list {
    margin: 20px 0 30px 20px;
  }

  .compliance-list li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .compliance-list li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .image-placeholder {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #27ae60 0%, #1a472a 100%);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 60px;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-white);
    min-height: 500px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .image-placeholder span {
    font-size: 6rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .image-placeholder p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .image-placeholder {
      min-height: 300px;
      padding: 40px;
    }

    .image-placeholder span {
      font-size: 4rem;
    }
  }
</style>
